Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:50.78,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Seus corpos estão desaparecendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.64,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Por que?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.22,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Não vencemos?!
